{"tid":1209423,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"URGENT 要求整合全港警犬及家人名單送往各國領事館","createTime":"2019-06-12T11:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T11:26:58.000Z","uid":7678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b41a06c7962d0a0474d205d8268a56cc0bcff97e","tid":1209423,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"認真問 - 有無人join?<br />\n<br />\n1. 搜集各警濫用武力證據 - 最好有相有片<br />\n2. 有警員編號、全名及最好有清晰面照<br />\n3. 將資料整合 - 將名單一一送往英美歐盟各國領事館要求表態<br />\n4. 一直廣傳名單 - 每日推，務求每個香港人都知自己身邊既警犬姓甚名誰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pinnpip.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPinnpip.png&h=ef568632&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W6KdvYt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW6KdvYt.png&h=613984b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FYefp8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FYefp8.png&h=85d0d764&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqQcMwR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqQcMwR.gif&h=64181c3b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}